column5: On my way home last night there were more than a few snowmobile tracks, both on the road, through the fields, and forest too.  I would almost say that there is the same amount of snow now as there was mid-January last year.  A little surprised / impressed.  Entropy
Yeah, I need to invest in a ice fishing sled, but the insurance always puts a hult to that idea.  But we all know how fast the snow can come and go. Almost as fast as money.
